Troubleshooting Database Corruption
 
 
 
 
 
When your database gets corrupted, one of the most important things to do is  figure out why that happened , so that you can try to ensure that it doesn't happen again.  After all, there's little point in going to a lot of trouble to restore a corrupt database from backup, or in attempting to repair the damage, if it's just going to get corrupted again.  However, there are times when root cause analysis must take a b